---
import MarketingLayout from '../../layouts/MarketingLayout.astro';
---
<MarketingLayout title="FAQ | Website Factory" description="Answers for local business owners considering a professional website launch.">
  <section class="content-section"><div class="container prose">
    <p class="eyebrow">FAQ</p>
    <h1>Questions before investing in a better website</h1>
  </div></section>
  <section class="content-section muted-bg">
    <div class="container faq-grid">
      <article class="faq-card"><h2>What makes this worth $3,500+?</h2><p>The package includes strategy, copy structure, design polish, local SEO basics, contact flow, deployment, and revision time. It is built to help prospects understand and trust the business faster.</p></article>
      <article class="faq-card"><h2>How much do I need to provide?</h2><p>Bring business details, service notes, locations, photos if available, testimonials, and the best way for prospects to contact you. The project turns those inputs into a clear site.</p></article>
      <article class="faq-card"><h2>Can this grow later?</h2><p>Yes. The first launch can be expanded with service pages, city pages, new galleries, seasonal promotions, and stronger proof over time.</p></article>
      <article class="faq-card"><h2>Do you handle hosting?</h2><p>Yes. The launch can be deployed to a static host such as GitHub Pages, Cloudflare Pages, or Netlify.</p></article>
    </div>
  </section>
</MarketingLayout>
